### ============================
### REQUEST FLOW (User 2 requests access, User 1 approves/rejects)
### ============================

### User 2: Create access request to tracker owned by User 1
POST {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/{{tracker_id}}/access-requests
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_2}}

> {%
    client.assert(response.status === 201, "Create request failed");
    client.global.set("access_request_id", response.body.id);
%}

### User 1 (owner): List all access requests for tracker
# Requires: OWNER role
GET {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/{{tracker_id}}/access-requests?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### User 1 (owner): List with search by email
GET {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/{{tracker_id}}/access-requests?search=jane&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### User 1 (owner): Approve access request
# Requires: OWNER role
PATCH {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/{{access_request_id}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### User 1 (owner): Reject access request
# Requires: OWNER role
PATCH {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/{{access_request_id}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### User 2: Cancel own access request
PATCH {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/{{access_request_id}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_2}}

### ============================
### INVITE FLOW (User 1 invites User 2, User 2 accepts/rejects)
### ============================

### User 1 (owner): Invite User 2 to tracker
# Requires: OWNER role
POST {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/{{tracker_id}}/access-requests/invite
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email2}}"
}

> {%
    client.assert(response.status === 201, "Invite failed");
    client.global.set("invite_id", response.body.id);
%}

### User 2: Accept invite
PATCH {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/{{invite_id}}/accept
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_2}}

### User 2: Reject invite
PATCH {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/{{invite_id}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_2}}

### User 1 (owner): Cancel own invite
PATCH {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/{{invite_id}}/cancel
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

### ============================
### MY REQUESTS
### ============================

### User 2: List all my access requests / invites
GET {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/mine?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_2}}

### User 2: Search my requests by tracker name
GET {{host}}/api/expense-trackers/access-requests/mine?search=Personal&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token_2}}